operations.description: Sends the given content to all the active WebSockets that match the path, socketType and groups criteria. In the case of the path, the base path configured in the config will not be considered as you may be targeting both inbound and outbound sockets. The message will be send to all the matching sockets, even though it's possible that delivery to some of them fail. The operation will return a list of BroadcastFailure containing details of each of the failures. If none fail, an empty list is returned
